    "Before moving to the applications, we describe in this section general approaches to augment tabular data for classification and regression problems with text data.",
    "Use NLP techniques to extract additional features from text data (each with a specific meaning understandable by humans).",
    "Add these additional columns to the tabular data already available and apply a supervised learning technique to the augmented tabular data.",
    "This approach is illustrated in Figure 4.",
    "Use NLP techniques to encode the text sequences into a finite set of additional columns, and proceed as in Approach A."
